{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PLEASE NOTE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Spell Casting is  free because it was made in 2016 using Construct 2 and I am no longer supporting the game.\u00a0 If it run and you can play it, great, but there is no need to submit any bug reports anymore as I cannot fix it.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spell Casting is a line drawing puzzle game in which you are a young wizard learning spells in the comfort of your home thanks to Wizardly Distance Education offered by the prestigious Magical Education Of Wizards School!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522990/extras/poem.png?t=1728337795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Practice casting spells by tracing out the patterns in the spell books using your mouse (or finger if using a touchscreen laptop / tablet). Earn a 3 star rating in each practice spell to unlock the exam for that book.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll need to remember the previously learned spell shapes to pass the exam and unlock new spell books!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spell Casting is fun for all ages and family friendly.  Play just for fun or try to achieve 5 stars in all the spells and exams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spell Casting supports accessibility by supporting touch screen tablet devices and also allows you to hold down the Space Bar when drawing instead of clicking the mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522990/extras/bookdesk.png?t=1728337795\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Burned Your Fingers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcom